</ul>

<p style="margin-left:48px; text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<ol start="2">
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Intellectual Property and other rights</span></span></strong></span></span></li>
